switchport mode trunk
switchport trunk native vlan 20
switchport trunk allowed vlan 5,10,15,20
no sh
exit
int range fa0/11-15
description Access kapcsolatok a vezetőségnek. / Access connections to the higher ups.
switchport mode access
switchport access vlan 15
no sh
exit
int range fa0/16-20
description Access kapcsolatok adminisztratív eszközöknek. / Access connections for administrative devices.
switchport mode access
switchport access vlan 20
no sh
exit
