exit
int fa0/24
description Az IBM_CNTRL_PRJCTPNS_S0 eszköz felé Trunk kapcsolat. / Trunk connection towards the IBM_CNTRL_PRJCTPNS_S0 device.
exit
int range fa0/11-20
spanning-tree portfast
exit
